'''[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]'''由數個主要部分構成，每個部門各司其職。主要的部門有地區巡邏部（Territorial Policing Directorate）、專門刑事部（[[:en:Specialist_Crime_Directorate|Specialist Crime Directorate]]）、特殊行動部（[[:en:Specialist_Operations|Specialist Operations]]）、中央行動部（[[:en:Central_Operations|Central Operations]]），及行政暨支援（administration and support）。每個部門皆由警察廳助理處長（[[:en:Assistant_Commissioner_of_Police_of_the_Metropolis|Assistant Commissioner]]）<!-- ,or in the case of administrative departments a director of police staff which is the equivalent civil staff grade.這句不會翻 -->負責監督。管理委員會則由警察廳總監（[[:en:Commissioner_of_Police_of_the_Metropolis|Commissioner]]，即廳長）、副處長（[[:en:Deputy_Commissioner_of_Police_of_the_Metropolis|Deputy Commissioner]]，副廳長）及各部門領導人組成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.met.police.uk/scd/specialist_units/policy_and_prevention.htm |title=Metropolitan Police Service – Specialist Crime Directorate |publisher=Met.police.uk |date= |accessdate=2009-05-29 |archiveurl=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20081105183429/http://www.met.police.uk/scd/specialist_units/policy_and_prevention.htm |archivedate=2008-11-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

